{"tid":656422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"16歲少女慘遭強姦後被報復燒死 印度警拘捕主謀及村長共15人","createTime":"2018-05-07T09:02:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T22:28:21.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c7f7100fd8fef3681cd8e4769577c022e6f56930","tid":656422,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T09:02:28.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】印度再傳出令人髮指的性暴力案件。警方昨日表示，東部加爾克漢德省 (Jharkhand) 1名男子強姦一名16歲少女後被告發及懲罰，因而心生不滿，闖入少女家中縱火，把她活活燒死。事件引發社會強烈反彈，印度警方今日表示，已拘捕主謀歸案。<br />\n<br />\n當地警方表示，少女家人上周四外出參加婚禮，2名歹徒從少女家中將她綁走，在加爾克漢德省 (Jharkhand) 森林地區強姦她。少女家人其後向當地村民委員會申訴，村委會下令被控強姦的歹徒罰做100下仰臥起坐，並罰款5萬盧比 (約5900港元)。由地方長老組成的村委會出面調解爭議，繞過印度冗長的司法制度。雖然村委會不具法律效力，但在鄉村地區影響力大。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，男子不滿村委會的懲罰，帶同多人闖入少女家中痛毆少女雙親，最後縱火將少女活活燒死。當地警方首長拉姆 (Ashok Ram) 向媒體表示：「被控的2人毒打少女雙親，闖入屋內，在同夥協助下向少女縱火。」<br />\n<br />\n當局隨即成立特別調查小組調查，派員特別保護少女的家人，並於今日宣布拘捕命案主謀布延 (Dhanu Bhuiyan)，當時他正藏在親戚家裡。此外，當局亦成立了醫療小組，將 (對受害者)進行驗屍。<br />\n<br />\n警方又表示，事發村落的村長亦因「宣布的懲罰導致這起凶殺案」而被捕。同時，至今共有15人涉案被捕。<br />\n<br />\n加爾克漢德省首席部長Raghubar Das亦譴責這種「野蠻」暴行，要求嚴懲凶手，並宣布給予受害者家人10萬盧比 (約11800港元) 補償。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/WUPlGBnAj4I_81AP8cabDQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/zh_hant_tw/News/bcc/hmz_20180507_0940.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FWUPlGBnAj4I_81AP8cabDQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh_hant_tw%2FNews%2Fbcc%2Fhmz_20180507_0940.jpg&h=e85a4d57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/16%E6%AD%B2%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E6%85%98%E9%81%AD%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6%E5%BE%8C%E8%A2%AB%E5%A0%B1%E5%BE%A9%E7%87%92%E6%AD%BB-%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95%E4%B8%BB%E8%AC%80%E5%8F%8A%E6%9D%91%E9%95%B7%E5%85%B115%E4%BA%BA-122900599.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F16%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%2585%2598%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%25A7%25A6%25E5%25BE%258C%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E7%2587%2592%25E6%25AD%25BB-%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E8%25AC%2580%25E5%258F%258A%25E6%259D%2591%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%2585%25B115%25E4%25BA%25BA-122900599.html&d=4tRPLw2x%2Bopihp7tnb4LpYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=0c823f6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/16%E6%AD%B2%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E6%85%98%E9%81%AD%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6%E5%BE%8C%E8%A2%AB%E5%A0%B1%E5%BE%A9%E7%87%92%E6%AD%BB-%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95%E4%B8%BB%E8%AC%80%E5%8F%8A%E6%9D%91%E9%95%B7%E5%85%B115%E4%BA%BA-122900599.html</a>"},{"pid":"345d359bace5bacf886f1cff7644e3a32ccd1ee4","tid":656422,"uid":140580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T10:15:06.000Z","msg":"村委會下令被控強姦的歹徒罰做100下仰臥起坐，並罰款5萬盧比 (約5900港元)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77451dfc5e5e25b12bd88497c5ef5b671be556fd","tid":656422,"uid":125237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T10:16:41.000Z","msg":"Cls國家"},{"pid":"483241cc39207cfad0be1ed75ab376db7c47d5e7","tid":656422,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"345d359bace5bacf886f1cff7644e3a32ccd1ee4","tid":656422,"uid":140580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T10:15:06.000Z","msg":"村委會下令被控強姦的歹徒罰做100下仰臥起坐，並罰款5萬盧比 (約5900港元)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T15:02:35.000Z","msg":"個村委真係對班人渣好好,完全係放生,不過班人渣仲係唔覺得自己錯左,仲走去燒